---
title: Nonna's Chicken Cotoletta & Tomato Salad with Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: This chicken cotoletta is extra special, with our garlic & herb seasoning cooked right into the cheesy crumb! It doesn’t need fancy accompaniments, a fresh tomato and balsamic salad is the perfect pairing. You’ll be thanking Nonna for sharing her best kept culinary secrets.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R35_W41_NZ_edit__MAIN_low-7066a01b.jpg
